0.1.name: wordpress/age-verify
0.1.description: Whatever your reasons, you may need your site's visitors to confirm their age before viewing the content of your site. Age Verify does just that. It's a simple plugin that lets you specify a minimum age and add an age-gate between a potential visitor and your content, just to be safe. Enjoy!
